/a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unaanaaneebooboo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Naanaan Eebooboo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/16/02 8:51:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=138.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Advice on training points please</span><hr size=1> You can only use training points to get to 20 skill in any of the tradeskills. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urochenko.showPublicProfile?language=EN>rochenko</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/16/02 9:04:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=138.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Advice on training points please</span><hr size=1> I've heard of people burning like 50-100 points on research though...isn't it a tradeskil?<br><br>Hraveob <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udaroob.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daroob</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/16/02 10:37:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=138.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Advice on training points please</span><hr size=1> Research is &quot;not&quot; a tradeskill.<br><br>If I were you, I wouldn't spend any points in tradeskills because the first few upgrades to any tradeskill are incredibly inexpensive.<br><br>Using your points in research is only beneficial if you are still trying to make your lvl 49 (or lower) spells.  If you're doing the shawl quest, I'm assuming you have these spells already or can buy them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=138.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=138.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=138.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=138.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm23.threadControl?topicID=138.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=138.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=138.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr>